text: Quain is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Buell Quain (1912–1939), American ethnologist *John Richard Quain (1816–1876), Irish barrister and judge *Jones Quain (1796–1865), Irish anatomist *Richard Quain (1816–1898), Irish physician *Richard Quain (1800–1887), English anatomist and surgeon ==See also== *An Examination of the Work of Herbert Quain, a 1941 short story by Argentine writer Jorge Luis Borges *Quain Professor, the professorship title for certain disciplines at University College, London, England
